%% FMS Guardrails Orchestrator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant GS as Guardrails Server<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Orch as Orchestrator Core
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS / caikit-nlp<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as vLLM / OpenAI<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 1: Text Content Detection (Unary)
    Client->>GS: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional), mTLS (optional)
    GS->>Orch: Route request
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk text (gRPC)<br/>TLS (configurable), mTLS (configurable)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>TLS (configurable), mTLS (configurable)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>GS: Aggregated response
    GS-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 2: Classification with Text Generation (v1)
    Client->>GS: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional), mTLS (optional)
    GS->>Orch: Route request
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text (gRPC)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (input detection)
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>TGIS: Generate text (gRPC)<br/>TLS (configurable), mTLS (configurable)
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (output detection)
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>GS: Classification + generation result
    GS-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 3: Chat Completions with Detection (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>GS: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional), mTLS (optional)
    GS->>Orch: Route request
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input detection)
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>TLS (configurable), Bearer token passthrough
    OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (output detection)
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>GS: Filtered response
    GS-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 4: Streaming Content Detection (NDJSON)
    Client->>GS: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>NDJSON stream, TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    GS->>Orch: Stream request
    Orch->>Chunker: Bidirectional streaming (gRPC)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments (streaming)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (per chunk)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>GS: NDJSON stream response
    GS-->>Client: NDJSON Response (streaming)
